title: Daughtry - Leave This Town [July 14, 2009] WEB_RIP
description:
This is DAUGHTRY's new album, Leave This Town, in stores July 14.  I'm bringing it to you early :).  This is a rip from VH1's website, so the quality isn't great.  Thought it would be good to share!


IF YOU LIKE THE ALBUM SUPPORT DAUGHTRY AND BUY IT ON JULY 14.  I KNOW I WILL!


From VH1:
"Chris and the guys' second album shares the life-changing experiences they've encountered on their journey to success. Listen to the entire CD a week before it's available in stores."
